locality: Ambatovy: Région Alaotra Mangoro, District Moramanga.
Dct. Ambositra, Com. Ambalamanakana, Fkt Ambatomainty, Inselberg Maharavana. Inselberg côté droit sur la route Ivato - Antoetra, ca. 19 km du sud-Est d'Ivato, ca. 5 km NO d'Antoetra.
Région: Atsinanana,District: Soanierana ivongo, Commune: Manompana.

Faritra Alaotra Mangoro, Fivondronana Moramanga, firaisana Ambohibary, fokontany Ampitabe, Ambatovy. Conservation zone, forest on crust. Récolté avec F. Edmond, R. Rakotondrajaona, K. Ralaisabotsy, S. Randrianasolo, M. Ratovoniaina.

Masoala Peninsula, Peak of Ambohitsitandroina, east of Ambanizan. Transect stations 8-12, at 100 m elevation increments, from 700 m to 1100 m altitude. Station 8 is the camp. Station 10 and 11 are no longer marked, thus the altitudes and stations are approximated.
Ambatovy: Région Alaotra Mangoro, District Moramanga.
NAnosy, Taolagnaro, Iaboko, Antsotso Avaratra. Foret Tsitongambarika.
